# Blazor Patterns

## UI Libraries

- **Radzen.Blazor** for UI controls (buttons, inputs, dialogs, layouts)
- **VisNetwork.Blazor** for graph/network visualizations
- **Fluxor.Blazor.Web** for state management (Redux pattern)
- **Blazored.LocalStorage** for client-side persistence

## State Management (Fluxor)

- State classes live in `Generator/Siteswaps.Generator/Components/State/`
- Follow the pattern: State record → Actions → Reducers → Effects
- Assemblies are scanned automatically via `ScanAssemblies` in DI setup
- Redux DevTools enabled only in `#if DEBUG`

## Component Organization

- Shared visualization components go in `Siteswaps.Components/`
- Generator-specific UI components go in `Generator/Siteswaps.Generator/Components/`
- Page components go in `Webassembly/Pages/`

## PWA / Deployment

- Published via GitHub Pages with `PublishSPAforGitHubPages.Build`
- Base URL: `https://siteswaps.passing.zone`
- Service worker support is enabled
